Choose over 25 different, customizable import racers. Each car has over 100 accessories available to improve your performance. Add a spoiler, upgrade the engine, tune the handling, change your wheels, add fog lights, even change the color. Beautifully rendered cars with realistic lighting (in this night time racing game, the street lights provide dynamic lighting effects. Incredible sense of speed - over 60 frames per second.
 
Encounter over 200 rival cars and drone trucks and cars while racing through Tokyo.  Non-linear highway system with a series of  on and off ramps that change the course/route in the middle of a race. Several different modes of gameplay available.